response.overview: Hopeless and dismal Ago Celaya runs for what's left of his fading life....or at least the life he knows. From disheveled street walker to blood thirsty night stalker watch the demented leathered cuck hunt Tucson's most talented skateboarders. Uncensored raw street skateboarding as it was meant to be seen. From brain hemorrhages to stone cold knockouts watch this disasterpeice unfold before your eyes.
response.tagline: You can't tell your friend you've been cuckolded, even if he doesn't laugh at you he may use it against you.
response.title: Cuck
